<LP>
   PALO ALTO, Calif. -- Tab Products Co. reported earnings
for its first quarter, ended Aug. 31, of $1.27 million, or 19
cents a share, little changed from $1.23 million, or 19 cents
a share, a year earlier. Revenue for the office-filing and
furniture-systems company declined about 2%, to $32.8 million
from $33.6 million.
