</GV>
<LP>
   A former billing clerk for L.F. Rothschild, Unterberg,
Towbin pleaded guilty to federal conspiracy and income tax
evasion charges.
   Joseph Andrews of Parsippany, N.J., told U.S. District
Judge Harold A. Ackerman that he stole more than $1 million
